    ComponentServiceI, DataTwoWayI, OfferedI, RequiredI, TwoWayI, InboundPortI, OutboundPortI, PortI, TwoWayPortI<DataTwoWayI>, java.io.Serializable, java.rmi.Remote

    public class PingPongDataTwoWayPort
extends AbstractDataTwoWayPort
    The class PingPongDataTwoWayPort implements the methods send of the DataTwoWayI.PushI interface, but throws an exception for the method request of the DataTwoWayI.PullI interface.

    Description

    Only the push interface is used.

    Invariant

     invariant              true
